{"snp2.1:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 2.1 ","snp2.1:0.2":"Ratanasutta ","snp2.1:1.1":"Yanidha bhutani samagatani, ","snp2.1:1.2":"Bhummani va yani va antalikkhe; ","snp2.1:1.3":"Sabbeva bhuta sumana bhavantu, ","snp2.1:1.4":"Athopi sakkacca sunantu bhasitam. ","snp2.1:2.1":"Tasma hi bhuta nisametha sabbe, ","snp2.1:2.2":"Mettam karotha manusiya pajaya; ","snp2.1:2.3":"Diva ca ratto ca haranti ye balim, ","snp2.1:2.4":"Tasma hi ne rakkhatha appamatta. ","snp2.1:3.1":"Yam kinci vittam idha va huram va, ","snp2.1:3.2":"Saggesu va yam ratanam panitam; ","snp2.1:3.3":"Na no samam atthi tathagatena, ","snp2.1:3.4":"Idampi buddhe ratanam panitam; ","snp2.1:3.5":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:4.1":"Khayam viragam amatam panitam, ","snp2.1:4.2":"Yadajjhaga sakyamuni samahito; ","snp2.1:4.3":"Na tena dhammena samatthi kinci, ","snp2.1:4.4":"Idampi dhamme ratanam panitam; ","snp2.1:4.5":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:5.1":"Yam buddhasettho parivannayi sucim, ","snp2.1:5.2":"Samadhimanantarikannamahu; ","snp2.1:5.3":"Samadhina tena samo na vijjati, ","snp2.1:5.4":"Idampi dhamme ratanam panitam; ","snp2.1:5.5":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:6.1":"Ye puggala attha satam pasattha, ","snp2.1:6.2":"Cattari etani yugani honti; ","snp2.1:6.3":"Te dakkhineyya sugatassa savaka, ","snp2.1:6.4":"Etesu dinnani mahapphalani; ","snp2.1:6.5":"Idampi sanghe ratanam panitam, ","snp2.1:6.6":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:7.1":"Ye suppayutta manasa dalhena, ","snp2.1:7.2":"Nikkamino gotamasasanamhi; ","snp2.1:7.3":"Te pattipatta amatam vigayha, ","snp2.1:7.4":"Laddha mudha nibbutim bhunjamana; ","snp2.1:7.5":"Idampi sanghe ratanam panitam, ","snp2.1:7.6":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:8.1":"Yathindakhilo pathavissito siya, ","snp2.1:8.2":"Catubbhi vatehi asampakampiyo; ","snp2.1:8.3":"Tathupamam sappurisam vadami, ","snp2.1:8.4":"Yo ariyasaccani avecca passati; ","snp2.1:8.5":"Idampi sanghe ratanam panitam, ","snp2.1:8.6":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:9.1":"Ye ariyasaccani vibhavayanti, ","snp2.1:9.2":"Gambhirapannena sudesitani; ","snp2.1:9.3":"Kincapi te honti bhusam pamatta, ","snp2.1:9.4":"Na te bhavam atthamamadiyanti; ","snp2.1:9.5":"Idampi sanghe ratanam panitam, ","snp2.1:9.6":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:10.1":"Sahavassa dassanasampadaya, ","snp2.1:10.2":"Tayassu dhamma jahita bhavanti; ","snp2.1:10.3":"Sakkayaditthi vicikicchitanca, ","snp2.1:10.4":"Silabbatam vapi yadatthi kinci. ","snp2.1:11.1":"Catuhapayehi ca vippamutto, ","snp2.1:11.2":"Chaccabhithanani abhabba katum; ","snp2.1:11.3":"Idampi sanghe ratanam panitam, ","snp2.1:11.4":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:12.1":"Kincapi so kamma karoti papakam, ","snp2.1:12.2":"Kayena vaca uda cetasa va; ","snp2.1:12.3":"Abhabba so tassa paticchadaya, ","snp2.1:12.4":"Abhabbata ditthapadassa vutta; ","snp2.1:12.5":"Idampi sanghe ratanam panitam, ","snp2.1:12.6":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:13.1":"Vanappagumbe yatha phussitagge, ","snp2.1:13.2":"Gimhanamase pathamasmim gimhe; ","snp2.1:13.3":"Tathupamam dhammavaram adesayi, ","snp2.1:13.4":"Nibbanagamim paramam hitaya; ","snp2.1:13.5":"Idampi buddhe ratanam panitam, ","snp2.1:13.6":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:14.1":"Varo varannu varado varaharo, ","snp2.1:14.2":"Anuttaro dhammavaram adesayi; ","snp2.1:14.3":"Idampi buddhe ratanam panitam, ","snp2.1:14.4":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:15.1":"Khinam puranam nava natthi sambhavam, ","snp2.1:15.2":"Virattacittayatike bhavasmim; ","snp2.1:15.3":"Te khinabija avirulhichanda, ","snp2.1:15.4":"Nibbanti dhira yathayam padipo; ","snp2.1:15.5":"Idampi sanghe ratanam panitam, ","snp2.1:15.6":"Etena saccena suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:16.1":"Yanidha bhutani samagatani, ","snp2.1:16.2":"Bhummani va yani va antalikkhe; ","snp2.1:16.3":"Tathagatam devamanussapujitam, ","snp2.1:16.4":"Buddham namassama suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:17.1":"Yanidha bhutani samagatani, ","snp2.1:17.2":"Bhummani va yani va antalikkhe; ","snp2.1:17.3":"Tathagatam devamanussapujitam, ","snp2.1:17.4":"Dhammam namassama suvatthi hotu. ","snp2.1:18.1":"Yanidha bhutani samagatani, ","snp2.1:18.2":"Bhummani va yani va antalikkhe; ","snp2.1:18.3":"Tathagatam devamanussapujitam, ","snp2.1:18.4":"Sangham namassama suvatthi hotuti. ","snp2.1:18.5":"Ratanasuttam pathamam. "}